<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink310">
<l>polampacum pāṇṭiṟ kācunirai yalku</l>
<l>lilaṅkuvaḷai meṉṟō ḷiḻainilai nekiḻap</l>
<l>pirital valluvai yāyi</l>
<l>ṉaritē viṭalaiyiva ḷāynutaṟ kaviṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>If you are capable of leaving [the girl] whose hips</l> 
<l>are covered with round coins [made of] green gold,</l>
<l>to make [her] jewels slip from the delicate shoulders, </l>
<l>[wearing] shining bangles,</l>
<l>strong man, the beauty of her fine forehead will become a rare [sight]. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
